ll vessel ischemic changes.</option></select></p><p><label> </label><input type=\"text\" name=\"enhancement?\" value=\"No abnormal enhancement.\"></p><p><label> </label><br><label>VENTRICLES/EXTRA-AXIAL SPACES: </label><input type=\"text\" name=\"ventricles-extra-axial\" value=\"No hydrocephalus or extra-axial fluid collections.\"></p><p><label>FLOW VOIDS: </label><select name=\"flow voids\"><option name=\"\" value=\"\">Intact.</option><option name=\"\" value=\"\">Not well assessed.</option></select></p><p><label>EXTRACRANIAL STRUCTURES: </label><input type=\"text\" name=\"extracranial\" value=\"Visualized structures are normal.\"></p></section><section data-section-name=\"IMPRESSION:\"><header class=\"Level1\">IMPRESSION:</header><p><textarea name=\"impression\">Normal contrast-enhanced MRI brain. </textarea></p></section></body></html>",
